INSERT INTO `article` VALUES ('33', '0', '关于希高智能科技有限公司', 'CTO所带领的研发团队在人工智能领域，移动通信，呼叫中心，语音识别，数据挖掘等相关技术领域深耕10多年。', '<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a href=\"http://www.ai-xg.com/index/index/company.html\">希高智能</a>位于江苏省淮安市浙大网新科技园31栋，分为技术研发体系、销售体系、服务运营三大体系。</span>CTO所带领的研发团队在人工智能领域，移动通信，呼叫中心，语音识别，数据挖掘等相关技术领域深耕10多年。<img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180810/1533882355407388.jpg\" title=\"1533882355407388.jpg\" alt=\"640.webp.jpg\" width=\"555\" height=\"394\"/></span></p><section><section><section><section><section><strong>完善的用户管理系统</strong></section></section></section></section></section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: left; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">让企业创建多个组或成员，进行资料管理和绩效掌控。</p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180810/1533882504428389.jpg\" title=\"1533882504428389.jpg\" alt=\"640.webp (1).jpg\" width=\"571\" height=\"350\"/></p><section><section><section><section><p><strong>智能语音识别和对答</strong></p><p><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px;\">颠覆传统自动外呼只能播放语音的问题，系统支持模拟行业专家与目标客户进行通话，让你拥有复制精英销售的能力。</span></p></section></section></section></section><section><section><section><section><section><strong>自动外呼功能</strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></section></section></section></section></section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: left; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">直接将客户号码导入，瞬间批量拨打客户电话，过程由呼叫平台自动完成，支持定时呼叫、筛选呼叫。</p><section><section><section><section><section><strong>客户资料管理功能</strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></section></section></section></section></section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: left; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">系统提供全程详实的通话录音，呼出了多少，哪个客户没有接通，接通时长，邀约是否成功，客户购买意向等统统记录在系统中，您可随时进行查阅、导出、统计等操作。</p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180810/1533882548456570.jpg\" title=\"1533882548456570.jpg\" alt=\"640.webp (3).jpg\" width=\"630\" height=\"406\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">对比其他同行，除市面上公有NPL系统（自然语言处理），我们希高智能自主研发Ai学习提升系统，让机器人每天都在进步。</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: left; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">我们是一家让人类专注创新，从重复枯燥的工作中解放出来，帮助企业搭载<span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px;\">人工智能，降低成本，提高效益，做一家助客户成功，让员工满意的公司。</span></p><p><br/></p>', '58', '15', '0', '1533886498');
INSERT INTO `article` VALUES ('34', '0', '什么是人工智能语音机器人', '电话机器人获得客户为人类3-4倍，工作时间内不用休息，24小时无间断呼叫客户，让潜在客户第一时间听到公司动态，使得工作效率得到翻倍提升。     企业经营成本下降', '<p class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0pt; padding: 0pt; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0pt; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 宋体;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 如今，在这个人工智能飞速发展的时代，</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt; letter-spacing: 0pt; text-indent: 0pt;\">各行各业都在与人工智能联手，寻求更好的发展与突破，电销行业也不例外。</span></p><p class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0pt; padding: 0pt; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0pt; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 全自动智能语音电话机器人的出现让电销企业看到了一道业绩突破的希望曙光，很多依赖电销做业绩的企业已经纷纷使用了全自动智能语音电话机器人，但是还有一些人在观望</span>;</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt; letter-spacing: 0pt; text-indent: 0pt;\">今天就让我们来了解一下什么是人工智能。</span></p><p><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180810/1533882704635953.jpg\" title=\"1533882704635953.jpg\" alt=\"640.webp (4).jpg\"/></p><p class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0pt; padding: 0pt; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0pt; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 人工智能，英文简写为</span>AI，</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt; letter-spacing: 0pt; text-indent: 0pt; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">是用于</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt; letter-spacing: 0pt; text-indent: 0pt;\">模拟、延伸和扩展人智能的理论、方法、技术及应用系统</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt; letter-spacing: 0pt; text-indent: 0pt; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">的一门新的技术科学。</span></span></p><p class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0pt; padding: 0pt; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0pt; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 人工智能实际是计算机科学的一个分支，</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt; letter-spacing: 0pt; text-indent: 0pt; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">它企图了解智能的实质，并生产出一种新的能以人类智能相似的方式做出反应的智能机器，该领域的研究包括机器人、语言识别、图像识别、自然语言处理和专家系统等。</span></span></p><p class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0pt; padding: 0pt; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0pt; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt; letter-spacing: 0pt; text-indent: 0pt; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180810/1533883167662831.jpg\" title=\"1533883167662831.jpg\" alt=\"640.webp (2).jpg\"/></span></span></p><p class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0pt; padding: 0pt; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0pt; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt; letter-spacing: 0pt; text-indent: 0pt; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 现如今人工智能大发展，如今：无人超市</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">,无人驾驶，无人机物流...都在不断研发推出；让人工智能在生活与工作中服务于人类，无论是从节约人工成本，工作效率上，都大大远胜于传统人工，人工智能也将会是社会的主流。</span></span></span></p><p class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0pt; padding: 0pt; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0pt; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt; letter-spacing: 0pt; text-indent: 0pt; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 江苏希高语音智能电话机器人具有以下几个特点：</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt; letter-spacing: 0pt; text-indent: 0pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">&nbsp;</span></p><section><section><section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 具备真人语音</span></p></section><section></section><section></section></section></section></section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 可以通过精准的语音途径，群呼潜在的客户，高效率的完成了人工无法抵达的电话呼出量，可以在每天达到</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: Arial; letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">800-1000</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">通的呼出量。</span><br/></p><p></p><section><section><section><section></section><section></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 具有专家销售经验</span></p></section></section></section></section><p></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 可以根据语音及记录自主判断是否为意向客户，记录沟通的过程完成沟通回访，它还具有自主学习的功能，沟通的话术会不断自我完善，意向客户判断更准确。</span></p><p></p><section><section><section><section><section><section><section><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 0px; text-align: justify; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></section><section><section><section><section></section><section></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 工作效率得到提升</span></p></section><section></section><section></section></section></section></section><section><span style=\"font-size: 14px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px; text-align: justify; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"> &nbsp; &nbsp;电话机器人获得客户为人类</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: Arial; letter-spacing: 0px; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">3-4</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px; text-align: justify; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">倍，工作时间内不用休息，</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: Arial; letter-spacing: 0px; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">24</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px; text-align: justify; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">小时无间断呼叫客户，让潜在客户第一时间听到公司动态，使得工作效率得到翻倍提升。</span><br/></section><section><section><section><section></section><section></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 企业经营成本下降</span></p><p style=\"text-align: start; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0px; text-align: justify;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0px; text-align: justify;\">传统电话销售企业最大的成本是工资薪酬，智能语音机器人为公司节省了工资薪酬费培训费等等。</span></p></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><p></p><p class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0pt; padding: 0pt; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0pt; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt; letter-spacing: 0pt; text-indent: 0pt; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></span></span></span><br/></p><p><br/></p>', '58', '15', '0', '1533886520');
INSERT INTO `article` VALUES ('35', '0', '语音机器人？智能对话新时代！', ' 随着互联网的快速发展，新智能时代已经到来，企业、个人都是互联网与智能的受益者', '<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 从“人工智能”一词的提出到现在已经过去60多年了，它的成熟发展让人不免期待的同时也害怕被完全取代。现在智能语音机器人产品繁多，如何选择一个好的智能语音机器人产品呢？</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180810/1533883500734200.jpg\" title=\"1533883500734200.jpg\" alt=\"640.webp (6).jpg\" width=\"644\" height=\"457\"/></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; 随着互联网的快速发展，新智能时代已经到来，企业、个人都是互联网与智能的受益者，而它们的存在将持续影响我们的工作和生活。曾经在互联网创立之初，很多人都觉得网络信息共享是一件不靠谱的事情，在看不见摸不着的网络上交流，如果遇到问题很难得到解决。但现实是，互联网已经很好融入了我们的生活，看到如今发展成上市公司的百度，谷歌，有多少人悔青了肚肠？</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>什么是智能化科技？</strong></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; 智能化是现代人类文明发展的趋势，要实现智能化，智能材料是不可缺少的重要环节。智能材料是材料科学发展的一个重要方向，也是材料科学发展的必然。智能材料结构是一门新兴起的多学科交叉的综合科学。智能材料的研究内容十分丰富，涉及许多前沿学科和高新智能材料在工农业生产、科学技术、人民生活、国民经济等各方面起着非常重要的作用，应用领域十分广阔。</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>希高智能语音机器人应运而生！</strong></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;它可以适用于金融行业、汽车行业、房地产行业、电商行业，互联网、广告、咨询、化妆品、保健、亲情等一切有电话销售形式的行业。<br/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>人工智能侵占电销领域未来电销或将无人化？</strong></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; 面对这样的问题，相信有很多人都会带着这样的疑问看待电话机器人，甚至连电销人员也在怀疑自己是否会被人工智能取代。这个问题的答案当然是否定的，希高的诞生不但不会取代人类电销员的地位，反而可以起到督促员工努力提升业绩的作用。</p><p><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>希高智能</strong></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;致力于成为智能语音技术应用的领头羊，我们的使命就是帮助传统企业搭载人工智能，降低成本，提高效益 。我们始终坚信，专注细分市场战略是成就希高行业地位的基础。一个企业的发展，离不开新事物的诞生，而语音智能的逐渐成熟将成为企业发展的最新推动力。</p><p><br/></p>', '58', '15', '0', '1533887908');
INSERT INTO `article` VALUES ('36', '0', 'AI智能语音机器人能为企业创造什么样的价值？', '人工智能（AI）简单来说，就是要使机器能够胜任一些通常需要人类智能才能完成的复杂工作。', '<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 16px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;\">什么是AI智能语音机器人？</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;\">&nbsp; 智能语音机器人是语音交互、语义理解、机器学习等AI技术的一种应用。它可以替代一些繁琐的销售客服工作：比如在给客户打电话、做客户资料录入、初筛的工作上，可以大量节省人工成本，并且提升工作效率。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180810/1533887866156437.jpg\" title=\"1533887866156437.jpg\" alt=\"640.webp (1).jpg\" width=\"553\" height=\"348\"/></p><p><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 16px; text-align: left; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp; 凭借着强大的数据处理能力、深度学习能力和不会受情绪影响的特质，人工智能在服务领域开始发挥着越来重要的作用——增加安全性、减少处理时间、减少重复性工作和人为错误、提高自动化水平、精准获客和营销，实现自助式服务等。</span><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 16px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 16px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">希高智能语音机器人的特点</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;\">&nbsp; 江苏希高智能科技有限公司推出的智能语音机器人，它们拥有CRM系统、语音识</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;\">别、</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;\">语意理解等等强大功能，更好的服务客户，提高效率。基于大数据、云计算、神经网络、深度学习等技术，利用深度神经学算法和自然语意理解技术，通过电话实现真人式专家级的销售沟通体验，为企业节省大量的人力成本。&nbsp;例如金融行业对电话销售比较依赖，人工智能可以代替人工拨打推销电话。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><section><section><section><section><section></section></section></section></section></section><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180810/1533887893911786.jpg\" title=\"1533887893911786.jpg\" alt=\"640.webp.jpg\" width=\"666\" height=\"501\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; line-height: 30px; background: white; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">主要核心技术功能</strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; line-height: 30px; background: white; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">1.</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">对比人工</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">：</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;\">快速与客户多轮对话，声音更礼貌，情绪更稳定，有亲和力，不知疲倦，永不离职，全天自定义时间拨打，后台记录通话详情可随时进行查阅、导出、统计等便于管理。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; line-height: 30px; background: white; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">2.</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">语义理解</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">：</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">对文本内容进行结构化语法分析，并结合专业领域知识图谱和上下文信息进行语义理解和对话反馈。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; line-height: 30px; background: white; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">3.</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">语言采集</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">：</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;\">以人工录音为主，支持录音人选型，男女声音定制化，这一合成技术媲美真人发声自然流畅，富有感情。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; line-height: 30px; background: white; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">4.</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">安全智能</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">：</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;\">企业数据信息安全，所有数据加密传输、加密储存，适用于电销<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">、</span>催收、客服等场景，降低企业人工成本，提升业务效率。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 0px; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; line-height: 30px; background: white; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-indent: 32px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 现如今各行各业，产品的销售都离不开电销，电话营销的重要已不言而喻，而传统的电销工具已经不能满足现代社会的发展需求。人工智能电销机器人的诞生可以说是革命性技术突破。</span></p><p><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></span></p><p><br/></p>', '58', '15', '0', '1534907049');
INSERT INTO `article` VALUES ('37', '0', '选购智能电话机器人应该注意的问题', '智能电话机器人的选购问题你get到了吗? ', '<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; 在人工智能语音领域，各种智能电话机器人发展迅速，种类和品牌也层出不穷，但是对企业来说，对产品不够了解，而市场上的产品又大多良莠不齐，如何做出对的选择也是个难题，今天就来说一说，选购智能电话机器人应该注意哪些问题。</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; 电话机器人是一件拥有人工智能基因的高科技产品，从选购产品以及合作伙伴的角度出发，判断机器人的品质优劣，应注意产品功能、系统性能、技术实力、服务体系、公司情况5个基本原则。</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;<strong>一、产品功能</strong></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; 电话机器人的研发初衷是为了代辅助人工完成海量号码初筛、通知等简单重复的工作，同时记录分析通话内容智能判断客户意向。为了达到这个要求，优秀的电话机器人应具备以下能力：1、多线群呼能力;2、识别对话能力;3、意向判断能力;4、人机协同能力;5、CRM能力;6、运营能力;7、交付能力;8、产品迭代能力。以上功能在我们希高电话机器人中都有很好的表现。</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>二、系统性能</strong></p><section><section><section><section><section><section><section><section><section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong>1、可靠性</strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 2px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 在日常运营中，电话机器人是否会失灵、故障?更新频次是否稳定成熟?这些都是我们选择时候需要考量的要点。</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 2px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><section><section><section><section><section><section><section><section><section><section><section></section><section></section></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong>2、便捷性</strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 2px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 界面简洁明了;详细的操作手册;视频指导操作;简单易读的CRM数据可视化效果;话术配置操作简单;支持移动办公。</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 2px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><section><section><section><section><section><section><section><section><section><section><section></section><section></section></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong>3、效率</strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px;\">观看电话机器人的效率好不好，我们可以从呼叫能力以及专业能力来看，希高电话机器人在与人类对话的过程中有着超强的理解能力，语音识别准确率高达98%，响应时间在0.5s-0.8s，能以最快的速度对客户的语言进行处理和回复，且自我学习能力强。<a href=\"http://www.ai-xg.com/index/index/product.html\" target=\"_self\" title=\"希高智能\">希高智能</a>最大的亮点在于系统的稳定及功能齐全。如机器人可以实现自动外呼、自动应答、自动记录、自动分类，支持通话中打断、转接人工、变量、意向客户微信推送，可以识别男女性别，整通通话还可以实现语音及文字两个板块，方便企业回查管理。</span></p></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><section><section><section><section><section><section><section><section><section><section><section><section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;\"><strong>三、技术实力</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: left; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: left; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">智能核心技术自主研发能力强,像语音识别(ASR)、口语理解(SLU)、情绪识别、对话管理(DM)、自然语言生成(NLP)、文本生成语音(TTS)均为公司自研。</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: left;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><section><section><section><section><section><section><section><section><section><section><section></section><section></section></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;\"><strong>四、服务体系</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: left; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: left; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">建立7*12小时专属客服、专业的售前指导、机器人话术训练服务、AI营销咨询等纳入服务体系中，并逐步从产品销售转向解决方案销售，到跟踪效果的深度服务营销。</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: left;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><section><section><section><section><section><section><section><section><section><section><section></section><section></section></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;\"><strong>五、公司情况</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: left; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: left; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">作为一家人工智能高科技公司，希高智能一直在持续研发投入，不断优化提升产品性能。目前，希高电话机器人已升级到4.0版本，未来将持续更新优化。</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: left;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 2px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 2px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">面对同行业的竞争，希高智能之所以处于领先地位，最主要的原因就是有一支强大的研发团队在背后做支撑，无论是产品的使用、售后还是产品的升级，研发团队每天都在为之努力付出。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 2px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: left; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 2px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 2px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">人工智能如今发展得如火如荼，<a href=\"http://www.ai-xg.com/index/index/company.html\" target=\"_self\" title=\"希高智能\">希高智能</a>由于有着前期的雄厚技术积累，得以在快速变化的市场中快速转生，迅速释放在人工智能领域的潜力。我们有理由相信，已经成功转型高科技公司的希高智能未来还将会给行业带来更多惊喜。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 2px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180810/1533884469539975.jpg\" title=\"1533884469539975.jpg\" alt=\"640.webp (3).jpg\" width=\"667\" height=\"459\"/></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 2px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><section><section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px 10px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: left; letter-spacing: 2px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; SO，智能电话机器人的选购问题你get到了吗?</span>&nbsp;</strong></p></section></section></section><p><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px 10px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: left; letter-spacing: 2px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;\"><br/></span><br/></p></section></section></section><p><br/></p><p><br/></p>', '58', '15', '0', '1534908036');
INSERT INTO `article` VALUES ('38', '0', '希高智能这些七夕攻略刷爆朋友圈', '希高智能它具备智能逻辑引导能力以及更优秀的真实应答能力，在重视用户体验感受的基础上，有效实现企业成本的降低和效率与业绩的提升。', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 七夕到了，还需要人工打电话的朋友们在等待什么，希高智能带你飞！</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;在互联网时代，人工智能的发展是必不可少的。</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180822/1534906426409860.jpg\" title=\"1534906426409860.jpg\" alt=\"0.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(63, 62, 63); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 1.5px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 2; text-indent: 28px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(63, 62, 63); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 1.5px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 2; text-indent: 28px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">据前瞻产业研究院《人工智能行业市场前瞻与投资战略规划分析报告》指出，2017年中国人工智能核心产业规模超过<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: Calibri;\">700</span>亿元，随着国家规划的出台，各地人工智能相关建设将逐步启动，预计到<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: Calibri;\">2020</span>年，中国人工智能核心产业规模将超过<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: Calibri;\">1600</span>亿元，增长率达到<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: Calibri;\">26.2%</span>。报告认为，从产业投资回报率分析，智能安防、智能驾驶等领域的快速发展都将刺激计算机视觉分析类产品的需求，使得计算机视觉领域具备投资价值<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: Calibri;\">;</span>而随着中国软件集成水平和人们生活水平的提高，提供教育、医疗、娱乐等专业化服务的服务机器人和智能无人设备具备投资价值。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(63, 62, 63); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 1.5px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 2; text-indent: 28px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(63, 62, 63); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 1.5px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 2; text-indent: 28px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(192, 0, 0);\">人工智能产业是智能产业发展的核心</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">，是其他智能科技产品发展的基础，国内外的高科技公司以及风险投资机构纷纷布局人工智能产业链，加快实施新一代人工智能科学基础的关键技术系统集成研发，使那些研发成果尽快能够进入到开放平台，在开放使用中再一次把它增强完善。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 1.5px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; widows: 2; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 1.5px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; widows: 2; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp; 一年前，电话机器人兴起。然而那时的机器人，机械笨拙、前言不搭后语，与用户沟通特别费劲，基本不能帮助企业解决任何实际问题。更有些拙劣者，成为企业与用户之间沟通的笑话。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 1.5px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; widows: 2; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"> 经过一年的打磨，希高智能研发出了全新的智能电销机器人，以<span style=\"color: rgb(192, 0, 0); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">更真人化的智能交互</span>，让用户体验更舒服，终于实现了机器与人的流畅沟通。而这一类电话机器人，无疑<span style=\"color: rgb(192, 0, 0); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">更契合企业营销需求</span>。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 1.5px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; widows: 2; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 2px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; widows: 2; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 1.5px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; widows: 2; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 2px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; widows: 2; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 为了使我们的产品更加完善，我们调研过很多电销冠军，大家的共识是，用户抵触生硬的产品推介，他们关心的是产品与自身需求是否真的匹配，而在这一过程中，销售的“<span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 2px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; widows: 2; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(192, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">善解人意</span>”和“<span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 2px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; widows: 2; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(192, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">灵活应变</span>”就成为了成单关键。</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 2px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; widows: 2; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">我们希高智能可以为每一位客户量身定制话术，确保机器人与人的沟通更接近于真人。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;因而，当企业引入智能电销机器人时，我们必须思考它的沟通流畅度与灵活性。希高智能它<span style=\"color: rgb(192, 0, 0);\">具备智能逻辑引导能力以及更优秀的真实应答能力</span>，在重视用户体验感受的基础上，有效实现企业成本的降低和效率与业绩的提升。</span></p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180822/1534906572240147.jpg\" title=\"1534906572240147.jpg\" alt=\"324.jpg\"/></p><section><section><section><section><section><section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: left; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(160, 160, 160); font-family: PingFangTC-light;\"></span></p></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 2px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; widows: 2; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span><br/></p>', '58', '15', '0', '1534924550');
INSERT INTO `article` VALUES ('39', '0', '希高小编不过七夕啦！换个角度解读智能电销机器人', '今天就好好和大伙聊聊AI电话机器人的真正价值。', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">首先3-5年内那些流水线重复性的工作会率先被取代，比如客服、电话销售、作业员。之后5-10年内一些标准化的工作也会将会被彻底的取代<br/></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">——李开复</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 19px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; orphans: 2; text-align: center; white-space: normal; widows: 2; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">前言</strong><br/></span></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 2; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;\">2017年，国务院正式印发《新一代人工智能发展规划》，规划重点描述了AI+传统行业的展望和规划。随着人工智能的兴起，</span><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-family: 宋体; text-decoration: underline;\">自然语音和语音识别技术</span></strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;\">发展迅速，智能电销机器人也因此应运而生。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 2; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 2; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;\">提到电话机器人，很多人的第一反应是这东西要替代人工了，有很多人要失业了......</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 2; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 2; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;\">虽然这种描述的可能性的确存在，但这和真正的电销机器人的核心价值相去甚远，今天就好好和大伙聊聊AI电话机器人的真正价值。</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"></span><br/></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; orphans: 2; text-align: center; white-space: normal; widows: 2; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;\">电销机器人是企业业务流程精细化运营的产物。</span></strong></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; orphans: 2; text-align: center; white-space: normal; widows: 2; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;\"><br/></span></strong></span></p><p></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 2; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(12, 12, 12);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">它并</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; text-decoration: underline; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">不是人工的敌人</span></strong></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">，而是在座各位的电销助手。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 2; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 2; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(12, 12, 12);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(12, 12, 12); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">电销机器人</span><span style=\"color: rgb(12, 12, 12); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; text-decoration: underline; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">本质</span></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(12, 12, 12); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">依然是一个工具，</span><span style=\"color: rgb(47, 47, 47); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">在现阶段，电话机器人还不能完全取代人工，而是协助人工客服完成外呼工作中最重复繁琐的一步</span><span style=\"color: rgb(47, 47, 47); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">——</span><span style=\"color: rgb(47, 47, 47); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">在海量的号码中帮助企业</span><span style=\"color: rgb(12, 12, 12); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">过滤掉</span><span style=\"color: rgb(12, 12, 12); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">90</span><span style=\"color: rgb(12, 12, 12); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">％的无效客户</span><span style=\"color: rgb(47, 47, 47); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">，从而</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; text-decoration: underline; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">筛选出意向客户</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(47, 47, 47); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">。至于业务上签约等细节问题，机器人暂时无法代替人工坐席去完成。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 2; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(12, 12, 12);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(47, 47, 47); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 2; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(12, 12, 12);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(47, 47, 47); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180822/1534907725346544.jpg\" title=\"1534907725346544.jpg\" alt=\"23432.jpg\"/></span></span></p><p><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; widows: 2; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; widows: 2; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">调查数据表明，绝大多数的机器人采购来自于企业电销工作的</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; widows: 2; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; text-decoration: underline; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">精细化运营</strong></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; widows: 2; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">需求，他们迫切的想把陌拜外呼流程标准化并规模化，将人力沉淀在业务流程的后端，更多的转化和服务好高价值客户，以高价值客户为中心打造服务流程。</span><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 2; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 2; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;\">那些将电销机器人使用的出神入化的公司，没有一个企图用机器人替代人工的全部，而是将人工从繁琐无趣的外呼工作中解放出来，让他们专注在更有价值的部分。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; orphans: 2; text-align: center; white-space: normal; widows: 2; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;\"><br/></span></strong></span><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; orphans: 2; text-align: center; white-space: normal; widows: 2; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;\">电销机器人不仅可以改善业务流程，也可以改善人才体系</span></strong></p><p><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; orphans: 2; text-align: center; white-space: normal; widows: 2; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;\"><br/></span></strong></p><p><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; orphans: 2; text-align: center; white-space: normal; widows: 2; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;\"></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 2; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;\">利益相关的很多人并不会失业，反而他们要</span><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-family: 宋体; text-decoration: underline;\">升职加薪</span></strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;\">了。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 2; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 2; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;\">这可能是电销机器人最违反直觉的论断，但却也是最符合现实的论断。决定工资薪水的，永远是工作内容的</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体; text-decoration: underline;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">价值</span></strong></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;\">。以往的很多重复性外呼工作，现在已经有机器人可以胜任了，因此这群人被动的得到了更高价值的客户转化工作。要知道，以前他们可能需要自己打线索、自己跟进、自己记录、自己转化、自己逼单、自己服务......</span></p><p><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180822/1534907791527183.jpg\" title=\"1534907791527183.jpg\" alt=\"343535.jpg\"/><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; orphans: 2; text-align: center; white-space: normal; widows: 2; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;\"><br/></span></strong><br/></p><p><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; widows: 2; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">这对于销售的素养极高，每一个环节都十分的消耗意志力，你不能奢求他们在业务流程的“层层围剿”下还能</span><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 2; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-family: 宋体; text-decoration: underline;\">高效</span></strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; widows: 2; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">表现，因此让他们聚焦在客户转化的工作部分显然更加合理。转化客户的工作无疑能给公司带来更大的价值，升职加薪也就不足为奇了。</span></p><p><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; widows: 2; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; widows: 2; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; orphans: 2; text-align: center; white-space: normal; widows: 2; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">总结</strong></span></p><p><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; widows: 2; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; orphans: 2; text-align: center; white-space: normal; widows: 2; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></strong></span></p><p></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 2; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;\">电销机器人可以替代月薪4k的客服没错，但这不该是企业启用电销机器人的</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体; text-decoration: underline;\">核心立场</span></strong></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;\">，也不是战略定位所在。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 2; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 2; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;\">“</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;\">缩减成本”不是电销机器人的根本目的，宣称电销机器人可以代替人工客服来工作，以此省去这部分的人工成本。这其实有些本末倒置，也并不了解客户的真正需求。有很多客户问到机器人能不能替代人工进而省钱的问题，但这样的情况一般只发生在比较初级的人工外呼岗位上，</span></p><p><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; widows: 2; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; orphans: 2; text-align: center; white-space: normal; widows: 2; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></strong></span></p><p><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180822/1534907846273613.jpg\" title=\"1534907846273613.jpg\" alt=\"r355.jpg\"/><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; widows: 2; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; orphans: 2; text-align: center; white-space: normal; widows: 2; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></strong></span><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 2; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(47, 47, 47);\">互联网大数据时代、智能时代到来，你不接受、尝试、学习，不参与进来，那么未来将很快会被互联网和智能淘汰掉。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 2; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 2; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">文章的最后小编一定要说：七夕快乐！</span></p><p><br/></p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180822/1534907875472590.jpg\" title=\"1534907875472590.jpg\" alt=\"43435.jpg\"/></p><p><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; orphans: 2; text-align: center; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">邮票上的七夕：演绎牛郎织女的故事</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; orphans: 2; text-align: center; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; orphans: 2; text-align: center; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180822/1534907902156429.jpg\" title=\"1534907902156429.jpg\" alt=\"324.jpg\"/></span></p>', '58', '15', '0', '1534993266');
INSERT INTO `article` VALUES ('40', '0', '网红机器人是骗局？希高智能为您解答语音助手的水平究竟怎样', '希高智能让目标客户有较好的体验和感受。通话结束后立刻判断客户意向程度反馈给销售专家，由销售专家二次跟进。', '<p><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; widows: 2; font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">3月<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: Calibri;\">21</span>日，猎豹<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: Calibri;\">CEO</span>傅盛一口气发布了多款机器人产品，但值得注意的是，在发布自家产品之前，傅盛拆穿了交通银行的机器人娇娇和机器人索菲亚的人工智能对话都是</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; widows: 2; font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0.5px; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">假象</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; widows: 2; font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">。难道，网络中那些带有人工智能语音的机器人都是假的？</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; widows: 2; font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 1.5px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">网红机器人</span></span></p><p><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; widows: 2; font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 1.5px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; widows: 2; font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp; 2015年的时候，交通银行的智能机器人“娇娇”刷爆了网络，这款萌萌哒的机器人出现在交行的很多分行中，它可以通过</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; widows: 2; font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0.5px; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">语言识别、人脸识别、触摸交互、肢体语言等</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; widows: 2; font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">方式，开展迎宾、业务引导、业务查询等多种服务类型，而且还会唱歌、讲笑话、跳圈圈舞。面对用户的提问时，其超高的智能和机智的回答仿佛人类已经步入人工智能时代。</span></span></span></p><p><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; widows: 2; font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 1.5px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; widows: 2; font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></span></span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180822/1534920386111837.jpg\" title=\"1534920386111837.jpg\" alt=\"0.jpg\"/><br/></p><p><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 3px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 2; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">&nbsp; 但是据傅盛透露，娇娇是一个</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0.5px; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">真人的视频系统</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">，它的声音是通过变音软件把客服的声音变出来的，是客服通过摄像头坐在远程的监控室里，然后装扮成机器人。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 3px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 2; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 3px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 2; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">&nbsp; 相比娇娇而言，机器人索菲亚拥有更多的鲜花和掌声，作为</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0.5px; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">历史上首个获得公民身份的机器人</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">她红遍了全球，它的连珠妙语令人津津乐道，甚至还说过要毁灭人类的言论。就在同一天，索菲亚还出席了3月<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: Calibri;\">21</span>日的某次联合国会议，与主持人侃侃而谈。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 3px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 2; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180822/1534924218193434.jpg\" title=\"1534924218193434.jpg\" alt=\"RERRR.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 3px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 2; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 3px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 2; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; widows: 2; font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp; 但是傅盛爆料，索菲亚的有些言论是提前录制好的，满满的都是套路啊</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 3px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; widows: 2; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 3px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 2; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 3px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; widows: 2; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 3px; orphans: 2; text-align: center; white-space: normal; widows: 2; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 3px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; widows: 2; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 1.5px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">智能语音的真实水平</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 3px; orphans: 2; white-space: normal; widows: 2; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 3px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; widows: 2; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 1.5px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 3px; orphans: 2; white-space: normal; widows: 2; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 3px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 2; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">&nbsp; 如果娇娇和索菲亚都不能算是真正的人工智能话，那么如今人工智能的水平</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0.5px; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">究竟如何呢</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">？</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 3px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 2; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 3px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 2; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">&nbsp; 就像傅盛所说，现在全世界范围内没有一家公司可能做到类似于机器人娇娇那样的对话水平，随时被打断、无论距离有多远，声音中是否有噪音，而且多人一起说话，每句的语义能理解的那么清晰，这一定做不到。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 3px; orphans: 2; white-space: normal; widows: 2; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 3px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; widows: 2; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 1.5px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 3px; orphans: 2; white-space: normal; widows: 2; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 1.5px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">语言识别的困境</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 3px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; widows: 2; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 1.5px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></span></span><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 3px; orphans: 2; white-space: normal; widows: 2; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; widows: 2; font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp; 语言是一种主观性较强的表达方式，</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; widows: 2; font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0.5px; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">不同的人所采用的说话规则是千变万化的</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; widows: 2; font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">。这与计算机程序有明显的不同，而人们通过语言表达并不会完全受制于规则，能够自由的遣词造句，并以此来传递信息，更何况我们常用的汉语有着非常复杂的语法，而且有些时候，不同的语言顺序并不会影响语义，再加上大量的地方方言以及那些心照不宣的“暗语”和“梗”。想要通过一套人工智能语音体系来应对不同的用户，其难度可想而知</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 3px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; widows: 2; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 3px; orphans: 2; white-space: normal; widows: 2; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 3px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; widows: 2; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 3px; orphans: 2; white-space: normal; widows: 2; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 3px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; widows: 2; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 0.5px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp; 2017年11月15日，《新一代人工智能发展规划》暨重大科技项目在京启动，会上公布了首批共四家国家人工智能开放创新平台名单：</span><br/><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 0.5px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">① 依托百度公司建设自动驾驶国家新一代人工智能开放创新平台；</span><br/><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 0.5px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">② 依托阿里云公司建设城市大脑国家新一代人工智能开放创新平；</span><br/><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 0.5px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">③ 依托腾讯公司建设医疗影像国家新一代人工智能开放创新平台；</span><br/><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 0.5px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">④ 依托科大讯飞建设智能语音国家新一代人工智能开放创新平台。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 3px; orphans: 2; white-space: normal; widows: 2; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 3px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; widows: 2; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 0.5px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 3px; orphans: 2; white-space: normal; widows: 2; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 3px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; widows: 2; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 0.5px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 3px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 2; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;\">&nbsp; 从选方向上，也不难看出各大公司在人工智能领域的发力方向：</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">百度、阿里、腾讯、科大讯飞</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;\">各自在自动驾驶、智慧城市、医疗影像识别、语音识别都是各自最具建树的领域。同时，这四个方向，也将是中长期内，人工智能的主要发展方向。除了以上四家巨头，国内还有很多其他公司也在着重发展人工智能。</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 3px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 2; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 3px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 2; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;\">&nbsp; 2012年以来，智能语音产业快速发展，与移动终端、社会信息服务、网络信息搜索等产业方向融合逐渐加深，</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">江苏希高智能科技</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;\">就是这些产业的精华产品。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 3px; orphans: 2; white-space: normal; widows: 2; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 3px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; widows: 2; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 0.5px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></span></span></p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180822/1534924330347176.jpg\" title=\"1534924330347176.jpg\" alt=\"GGREGR.jpg\"/></p><p><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 3px; orphans: 2; white-space: normal; widows: 2; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 3px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; widows: 2; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 0.5px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 0.5px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; widows: 2; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp; 传统电销行业，为实现公司业绩最大化，只能增加更多的电销人员来实现目标。但是，随着人员的增加，企业的成本也越来越高。为什么要这样说呢，我们来算一笔账就知道了。企业每招来一个员工，需要付出</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 0.5px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; widows: 2; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">底薪+提成<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: Calibri; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">+</span>补贴<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: Calibri; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">+</span>管理<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: Calibri; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">+</span>加班费<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: Calibri; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">+</span>培训<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: Calibri; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">+</span>电话费<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: Calibri; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">+</span>办公耗材</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 0.5px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; widows: 2; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">等，这意味着什么，相必大家都已经猜到了！这种传统粗放的商业模式严重制约着企业的发展。</span></span></span><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 3px; orphans: 2; white-space: normal; widows: 2; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 3px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; widows: 2; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 0.5px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 0.5px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; widows: 2; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 3px; orphans: 2; white-space: normal; widows: 2; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 3px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; widows: 2; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 0.5px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 0.5px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; widows: 2; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 1.5px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">希高智能科技</span></span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 3px; orphans: 2; white-space: normal; widows: 2; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 3px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; widows: 2; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 0.5px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 0.5px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; widows: 2; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 1.5px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span></span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 3px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 2; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;\">&nbsp; 可以</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">替代销售专家</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;\">做第一通电话的意向客户筛选工作。通话过程中完全模仿销售专家的语音，情绪，向目标意向客户介绍。能与客户多轮互动，能挖掘客户需求，客户拒绝能挽回，客户有意向能缔结。让目标客户有较好的体验和感受。通话结束后立刻判断客户意向程度反馈给销售专家，由销售专家二次跟进。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 3px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 2; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 3px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 2; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">&nbsp; 帮助企业解决筛选意向客户难的困境。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 3px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 2; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 3px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 2; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">&nbsp; 人工智能时代，重复，繁琐，浪费时间和精力的工作交给希高智能机器人做，人工销售人员并不会失业，而是将更多精力放在意向客户身上，毫无疑问，业绩会因此大大提高。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 3px; orphans: 2; white-space: normal; widows: 2; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 3px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; widows: 2; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 0.5px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 0.5px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; widows: 2; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 1.5px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></span></span></span></span><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 3px; orphans: 2; white-space: normal; widows: 2; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 3px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; widows: 2; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 0.5px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 0.5px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; widows: 2; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 1.5px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></span></span></span></span></p>', '58', '15', '0', '1535015936');
INSERT INTO `article` VALUES ('41', '0', '空调之于夏日，话术之于智能语音机器人', '希高智能电销机器人是通过事先设置好的语音处理系统，然后根据客户需求，拟定对应的话术，并录入系统', '<p><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 1px;\">希高智能<a href=\"http://www.ai-xg.com\" target=\"_self\" title=\"电销机器人\">电销机器人</a>会主动拨通客户的电话，像真人一样，为客户介绍产品、回答客户的咨询问题。在人机对话中，最难的就是让机器人听懂并准确理解客户的语言，并迅速做出精确的回答。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"text-align: center;\">识别</span></strong></p><section><section><section><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>科大讯飞98%</strong></p></section></section></section><p><br/></p><section></section><section></section><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 1.5px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 1.5px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 2; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 1px;\">首先，机器人要听懂客户的语言，这靠的是语音识别准确率。现在百度、科大讯飞、阿里的语音识别接口已经放开，在识别准确率上，科大讯飞语音识别的准确率已经从2010年刚刚发布语音云时的60.5%升级到98%，语音合成技术在国际语音合成比赛Blizzard Challenge上取得12连冠的成绩。</span></p><section><section><section><section><strong>话术</strong></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;\"><strong>话术训练是电销机器人得灵魂</strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p></section></section></section></section><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; orphans: 2; text-align: center; widows: 2; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">如果AI技术是基础，那么话术训练就是灵魂</span></strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; orphans: 2; text-align: center; widows: 2; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; orphans: 2; text-align: center; widows: 2; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 1px;\">一方面，机器人的语言模式需要对其话术进行设置和训练，才可以达到好的效果。在具体的会话场景中，会产生大量重复性问题，我们要收集语料及关键词，将这些问题整理成知识库，这样机器人在遇到这些重复性提问时，就能快速自动应答。随着知识库越来越丰富，机器人能解答的问题就越来越多，客户体验也就越好。</span></p><p><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; orphans: 2; text-align: center; widows: 2; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 1.5px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; orphans: 2; text-align: center; widows: 2; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180827/1535354686401447.jpg\" title=\"1535354686401447.jpg\" alt=\"433.jpg\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; orphans: 2; text-align: center; widows: 2; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; orphans: 2; text-align: center; widows: 2; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 1.5px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 1px;\"> 当然机器人不只要会回答客户提问，还需要把握电销客户心理，会引导客户、最终达成意向。所以我们需要通过话术设置，以不同的问法引导客户回复，方便机器人理解。每个公司身处的电销领域不同、业务不同、活动政策也不同，注定了话术的不同，有针对性才能贴合公司实际需要，话术定制涉及机器人语言设计、知识库的丰富，还需要通过无数次测试检验，保证机器人能够准确应答，不错失意向客户。</span></p><p><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; orphans: 2; text-align: center; widows: 2; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 1.5px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></span></span></p><p><br/></p><section><section><section><section><strong>江苏希高智能</strong></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;\"><strong>您的话务专家</strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 26px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 1.5px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 2; line-height: 30px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 1px;\">我们的电销机器人是通过事先设置好的语音处理系统，然后根据客户需求，拟定对应的话术，并录入系统。企业订购我们的电销机器人之后，销售会发送给企业一套话术的模板，将平时人工销售与客户之间交流的对话记录在话术上。话术发送给录音师，录音师会对其进行修改，将话术修改的更加自然和贴近生活，然后给企业进行查看。</span></p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180827/1535354829127764.jpg\" title=\"1535354829127764.jpg\" alt=\"234.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 26px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 1.5px; orphans: 2; text-align: center; white-space: normal; widows: 2; line-height: 30px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 1px;\">话术可录入，对话更精准</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 26px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 1.5px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 2; line-height: 30px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 1px;\">企业满意后，我们专业的录音师开始进行录音，经过录音师多次的练习和录音后，我们的技术人员会将状态最好的话术上线。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 26px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 1.5px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 2; line-height: 30px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 1px;\">话术上线后，我们的技术人员会在此基础上进行测试、修改、测试……</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 26px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 1.5px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 2; line-height: 30px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 1px;\">经过多次的调试和修改之后，确定机器人出错的概率达到最小，机器人最终上线，开始为企业工作。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 26px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 1.5px; orphans: 2; text-align: center; white-space: normal; widows: 2; line-height: 30px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 1px;\">机器人学习，话术可改进</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 26px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 1.5px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 2; line-height: 30px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 1px;\">我们的<a href=\"http://www.ai-xg.com\" target=\"_self\" title=\"电销机器人\">电销机器人</a>还有一个优势就是会进行学习，在与客户对话的过程中会把客户咨询的没出现过的关键词把文字保存下来。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 26px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 1.5px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 2; line-height: 30px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 1px;\">我们的技术人员再进行话术修改的时候会将这些关键词添加进系统，让机器人可以更加精准的定位客户。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p></section></section></section></section>', '58', '15', '0', '1535357320');
INSERT INTO `article` VALUES ('42', '0', '时代在召唤，智能语音机器人预备备！', '电销是每个企业不可或缺的一股销售力量，其优势就是让企业和客户在未见面的前提下就能建立合作意向，相比跑外寻找  客户要方便很多', '<p>&nbsp;时代的发展、进步实在是太快了，百年以前还是靠人力做事，几十年后就在靠机器，现在的我们必须要不断的学习积累知识，以防社会把</p><p><br/></p><p>我们给抛弃了，电销是每个企业不可或缺的一股销售力量，其优势就是让企业和客户在未见面的前提下就能建立合作意向，相比跑外寻找</p><p><br/></p><p>客户要方便很多，同时，电销在企业中的弊端也极为突出，人工成本高，工作效率低.......</p><p><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>智能语音机器人的现状</strong></p><p><strong><br/></strong></p><p>国际上对机器人的概念已经逐渐趋近一致。一般来说，人们都可以接受这种说法，即机器人是靠自身动力和控制能力来实现各种功能的一</p><p><br/></p><p>种机器。联合国标准化组织采纳了美国机器人协会给机器人下的定义：“一种可编程和多功能的操作机；或是为了执行不同的任务而具有可</p><p><br/></p><p>用电脑改变和可编程动作的专门系统。”它能为人类带来许多方便之处！最近有80%企业里出现了电销机器人，为此电销人员表示恐慌也表</p><p><br/></p><p>示欢迎！</p><p><br/></p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180827/1535356477537050.jpg\" title=\"1535356477537050.jpg\" alt=\"0.jpg\"/></p><p><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>智能语音机器人的优点</strong></p><p><strong><br/></strong></p><p>机器人电话销售系统既可以用于电话销售活动，同时还能广泛用于市场调查推广，业务受理、来电咨询、来电投诉等各种电话服务行业。</p><p><br/></p><p>机器人电话销售系统不仅可以大大节省人力资源，还可以促进业务的自动化和规范化。在节省费用的同时，还能够极大的提高效率。</p><p><br/></p><p>1、她是一个只会工作从不抱怨的好员工；</p><p><br/></p><p>2、她不用发工资只要充电就行；</p><p><br/></p><p>3、她比您最优秀的电话销售员工都更专业；</p><p><br/></p><p>4、她一天的工作量是您五个员工的总和，一天1000次有效电话；</p><p><br/></p><p>5、她不会提离职，不会生气，不会闹情绪；</p><p><br/></p><p>6、她能学会你教她的任何技能永远不会忘记；</p><p><br/></p><p>7、她会越来越聪明，越来越有工作效率。</p><p><strong><br/></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>人工智能的未来</strong></p><p><br/></p><p>人工智能正在悄悄改变我们生活的时代一个高科技的产品问世就等于大大提高了我们的生活质量和工作质量。虽然如今的人工智能仍然有</p><p><br/></p><p>不完美的地方，但我相信通过人类的不断努力，人工智能在未来的发展会有无限可能。亦如我们的希高一样会给大家带来更多的惊喜！</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><br/></strong><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180827/1535356586167152.jpg\" title=\"1535356586167152.jpg\" alt=\"462.jpg\"/></p><p><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>总结</strong></p><p><strong><br/></strong></p><p>新一代智能电销机器人的出现，有效解决了这些痛点。只需电销人员导入行业标准话术，我们的电销机器人即可大展神威。它能够主动外</p><p><br/></p><p>呼客户，通过领先的智能语音交互技术实现机器人与用户无障碍语音交流，并将客户反馈信息收集记录。</p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p>另外，智能电销机器人能够时刻保持统一标准、热情礼貌的语音沟通，并快速准确答复客户业务问讯，还能批量呼叫客户，无需休息吃</p><p><br/></p><p>饭，大大节约了人力成本，提升了电话营销的效率，实现电销效率质变。</p><p><strong><br/></strong><br/></p>', '58', '15', '0', '1535357944');
INSERT INTO `article` VALUES ('43', '0', '人工智能语音机器人是如何做数据管理的？', '', '<p>人工智能这个话题我们都不陌生了，但是还有很多朋友对人工智能语音机器人不太理解，甚至存在误解。语音机器人是相当于我们企业的<strong>客服/销售</strong>一职，不单单是语音，重要的是对话。</p><p><br/></p><p>像真人一样，跟客户聊天、谈业务。说到这里，很多朋友就会感到疑惑，机器还会像人一样思考？这个语音机器人是如何做到数据管理的？下面我们请负责希高智能科技的技术人员为我们解答：</p><p><br/></p><p>希高智能机器人之所以能实现聊天，对话，谈业务，不是因为人工智能语音机器人能思考，而是后台程序设定很完善。当语音机器人的话术设定好之后，结合外呼技术，机器人自动拨出电话，然后根据程序设定，跟客户交谈。</p><p><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(91, 151, 186); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">人工智能客服机器人</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(91, 151, 186); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></span></p><p>语音机器人做数据管理是有一套管理系统，比如说我们的希高智能语音机器人，在第一次筛选客户的时候会有这样一个过程：<strong>拨出电话→接听→通话→挂断→标签分类→云端存储</strong>，筛选完之后会再根据标签来进行二次沟通。</p><p><br/></p>在这些过程里，每一个流程就会自动完成记录一次，<strong>拨出电话记录→接听情况记录（没有接是因为网络问题还是挂断还是无法接听等）→通话时长、通话录音、通话文字记录→系统根据通话内容自动生成标签将客户分类存储→所有数据加密保存上传云端。</strong>机器人做好了数据管理，在下一次拨出电话时，就能更加高效的联系客户，成单率也更高。<p><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 13px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(91, 151, 186); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180827/1535357560732691.jpg\" title=\"1535357560732691.jpg\" alt=\"345436.jpg\"/></span><br/></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(91, 151, 186); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></span></p>语音机器人管理好的数据对于我们人工来说就不只是看看而已，这些数据是我们对机器人的一个把控，并且数据也要及时查看，如果机器人在与客户通话的时候出现新的问题，机器人回答不上来，那么我们就要及时反馈，录入新的话术，下一次在遇到类似的问题就不会回答不上来了。<p><span style=\"color: rgb(91, 151, 186); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(91, 151, 186); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(91, 151, 186); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">希高智能语音机器人功能</span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(91, 151, 186); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(91, 151, 186); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></span></span></p><p>我们的语音机器人在正式工作前，只需要培训一周，需要行业专业人员将话术整理好，录入机器人后台系统，然后多次拨出测试，争取在上岗前做到对答如流！当然，在测试的过程中要从不同角色来测试，要不断的给他出难题，才能让他更快的成长进步！</p><p><br/></p><p>测试语音机器人的时候还会根据情况<strong>生成不同的标签</strong>，这个标签在后面上岗后也是有大用处的，就可以为机器人省下更多的时间来专心工作。所以前期的测试工作一定要认真做才行！</p><p><br/></p><p>机器人的工作内容都<strong>有数据在后台，可以随时查看，并且数据可导出</strong>，方便人工查看。我们的希高智能语音机器人也会分析数据，这样我们去查看的时候一眼就知道今天打出了多少个电话，有多少个意向客户，有哪些需约了面谈，这样一来，我们的工作效率也会大大提升，不用每天都坐在办公室打电话，直接联系意向客户谈成单才是销售应该做的。</p><p><br/></p><p>希高智能机器人的技术告诉我们，话术设定也是有一套专业的程序，话术首先是由本行业的金牌客服来进行整理，在开场白之后整理方向是由客户心理来走的，大致分为这四种心理：<strong>肯定、否定、中性、拒绝。</strong></p><p><br/></p><p>一般语音机器人提供语义识别技术，识别到这四种态度就会很准确的判断，如果是超出这四种设定，还有一种随意设定，如果是问语音机器人的年龄，她就会做随意设定设定处理，当然，这些设定都是由人来完成的。</p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p>', '58', '15', '0', '1535458865');

